    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >生存</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到Backrooms。在这个临界世界中，你必须保护前哨基地免受各种实体的威胁，最重要的是，你必须生存下来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101910/extras/40c73794df4f5c7eaf869b1d373b9cd6.poster.avif?t=1732032175\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101910/extras/40c73794df4f5c7eaf869b1d373b9cd6.webm?t=1732032175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101910/extras/40c73794df4f5c7eaf869b1d373b9cd6.mp4?t=1732032175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >有限资源</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过摄像头观察周围环境，使用灯光驱逐生物，必要时锁门保护自己。但别忘了！前哨基地的能量有限，如果消耗殆尽，你可能要面对这些实体。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101910/extras/4cc3bdabdea7cf0c92d590fcffd3b5bf.poster.avif?t=1732032175\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101910/extras/4cc3bdabdea7cf0c92d590fcffd3b5bf.webm?t=1732032175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101910/extras/4cc3bdabdea7cf0c92d590fcffd3b5bf.mp4?t=1732032175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与商人交易</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以用赚来的钱在商店里购买工具。或者，你可以在夜晚经过前哨的商人那里以合理的价格购买。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/s